                        <item xml:id="e1">- Short hymns and supplications (ʾaryam, mäwaśǝʾt, mǝlṭan, etc.), performed for the funeral of different categories of Christians (fols. 120ra l.17 – 122rb l.22) are written in smaller script.&#xD;
- Pen trials (the bottom one dated "Monday, Gǝnbot 28"): fol. 2r. &#xD;
